{"type":"message","id":"e9445989","parentId":"aef2f1f9","timestamp":"2026-03-18T06:58:35.789Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"根据日志，我看到之前 3/16 有一次重启，是通过 feishu 插件调用 gateway restart 进行重启的。日志显示重启成功了（重启后重新连接）。\n\n现在用户说\"网关重启失败了\"。从之前的状态检查来看，网关当前是运行的（RPC probe ok）。但有一个 lock 文件 (gateway.f9aa0244.lock)，时间是今天 14:52 (北京时区)。\n\n让我看一下这个 lock 文件的 PID 是否对应一个进程。如果进程已经不在了，那可能之前确实有重启失败的情况。但现在网关是运行的，说明可能后来又自动恢复了。\n\n让我检查一下 lock 文件中提到的 PID 13792 是否还活着：","thinkingSignature":"3cc6647da9b99e67bb88ddd1eca002a4a24b89c567a97257be3090f456220188"},{"type":"text","text":"让我检查一下 lock 文件中提到的进程状态：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tm5uv0544v96_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"Get-Process -Id 13792 -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Id,ProcessName\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":72659,"output":204,"cacheRead":37249,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110112,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773817104601}}
